(1. Introduction To The Topic) Tj
T*
(Java is a structured object-oriented programming language used in many applications. In) Tj
T*
(a textbook lesson, the first goal is to make the computing concept clear. Students) Tj
T*
(should be able to explain what Java means, identify where it appears in Computer) Tj
T*
(Science, and describe the main purpose of the topic without relying on memorized) Tj
T*
(sentences.) Tj
